        <div class="generic-html-block ej-text" style="background: url()  no-repeat bottom left;">
    <span style="color: #ffffff;">
</span>
<p style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">We believe in being open and up front with customers, so we have developed our Privacy Promise, a quick and simple summary explaining how we manage, share and look after your information.</span></p>
<span style="color: #ffffff;">
</span>
</div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-spacer"></div>
